{"tid":1461100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"救解決連儂銀紙方法（中銀）","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:51:52.000Z","uid":124045,"like":171,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"bf53773d76f38b8e3d9831c9833e8049423e8142","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:14:24.000Z","msg":"邊L個搞銀錢&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460854</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n就住以上個post既內容<br />\n我會再檢視一下自己銀紙有冇被寫上任何字<br />\nAs i said la 一陣用唔到點算呢<br />\n作為一個香港市民<br />\n使用合法既鈔票係非常重要<br />\n<br />\n點知比我發現今日食飯找續返黎既中銀既紙幣<br />\n上面被寫上左<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港警察 知法犯法 <br />\n等等既字句<br />\n<br />\n正如我上面所講 <br />\n維持香港銀紙既流動性係非常之重要<br />\n同時銀紙既合法性都係非常重要<br />\n當下我必需立即止暴制亂咁<br />\n去發鈔銀行（中銀）換返合法既鈔票<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎啦<br />\n大家試想像下<br />\n如果不同角色係大量發鈔銀行鈔票被寫上不同字句<br />\n鈔票既流通性會點？<br />\n發鈔銀行既發鈔成本會點？<br />\n發鈔銀行更換貨幣既人手又會點？<br />\n大家要諗一諗 唔好影響到普通市民同銀行員工既日常生活同工作<br />\n<br />\n特此 本人強烈譴責暴徒弄污鈔票<br />\n以及呼籲香港市民共同齊心解決呢個問題"},{"pid":"9def91dd5e1f9b8c625c0ad8c32e66b61260f07a","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"各位市民請檢查自己既紙幣"},{"pid":"bf0fe73add2cb914a5e8a306eb1ce43d9142d309","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:15:06.000Z","msg":"唔好助長暴徒"},{"pid":"0fabfc1731316542195f19b9e96108336fb7439d","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:15:38.000Z","msg":"切勿協助暴徒傳播不實字句"},{"pid":"f5db179d1de95bac2ae30b911015bfb70a1fa935","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"香港市民應該齊心向前"},{"pid":"f04d00db39eb398b9b6e9b629eda2817890ecd99","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:11.000Z","msg":"共同守返法治"},{"pid":"86e345f8875ab9381aa4fbc36a53e036b46d7474","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"止暴制亂"},{"pid":"5725b31c8568c4f0befc8868356b0293972ef26a","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:43.000Z","msg":"讓香港保持繁榮"},{"pid":"1ee5ef2d5fbb10f303c6f68c15f11d030d7bfa41","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:01.000Z","msg":"守護銀紙"},{"pid":"c74f3873959a875dabc402809c29b25ab8b5a94b","tid":1461100,"uid":61680,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c387cc34696b8b6aec8cbdde2f994fdf6711be","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:12.000Z","msg":"人人有責"},{"pid":"9a18514bd0fe571b7c393fd05871993aeb526bb1","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"同時呼籲市民"},{"pid":"ca9a96d88738f5396eda6d81962b6ef28869dab0","tid":1461100,"uid":61882,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"唔知如果印&ldquo;堅定支持中國共產黨依法治國治港&rdquo;<br />\n銀行收唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31025f0ba90573f4e6c213536ed5edbc46523094","tid":1461100,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"睇到好躁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712611ea4016a8ff035328e71727e5ac61fc1480","tid":1461100,"uid":254361,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:20:47.000Z","msg":"中銀定渣打呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n行動前，用腦諗下，要自主思考呀<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n同埋連登被滲透之下<br />\n各種謠言滿天飛，更加要冷靜思考<br />\n要多方面去驗證嗰篇文是否真實<br />\n再去諗下佢發呢個信息個目的係乜嘢<br />\n諗下佢背後有沒隱藏的意思（例如恐慌、煽動、造謠）<br />\n<br />\n和理非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」「V怪客」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里的大反派說了這麼幾句<br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以用你的力量與聲音，用你的方法去「抗爭」<br />\n力量聲音沒分大細，沒分方法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（細音說，方法有分成本與效益）<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"39c6fe6d928baec01e260d7a250463ce4dc1ec08","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"香港有三間發鈔銀行 <br />\n<br />\n匯豐 渣打 及 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中銀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n中銀分行最方便 <br />\n大家可以檢查中銀既銀紙先！"},{"pid":"2bb80a5c513609fe299aef7773a84a8f306e8529","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c74f3873959a875dabc402809c29b25ab8b5a94b","tid":1461100,"uid":61680,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"要明既會明 唔明既點都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03bd02be6598cdcceb6af811e1d59c71e28a06d","tid":1461100,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8470ec7b05f95235704185bcca4cceaa44a99b7","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ca9a96d88738f5396eda6d81962b6ef28869dab0","tid":1461100,"uid":61882,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"唔知如果印&ldquo;堅定支持中國共產黨依法治國治港&rdquo;<br />\n銀行收唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:23:23.000Z","msg":"唔好寫任何字就最好啦！<br />\n你都知銀行回收同再發鈔都要時間同成本<br />\n<br />\n止暴制亂！"},{"pid":"6cdd1c6a2fbc5452d1695f88b8ebafc39ac580b1","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a03bd02be6598cdcceb6af811e1d59c71e28a06d","tid":1461100,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"銀行唔收？<br />\n發鈔銀行有必要更換比市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一陣比人當用偽鈔點算 <br />\n<br />\n幾大都去銀行驗下先"},{"pid":"367a1baa022941e680fcd21893614e60d3a5dfce","tid":1461100,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />白色恐怖<br />\n佢想凍結你個戶口"},{"pid":"0712a30aa6a25b125cbe872066c12b4358fd61e2","tid":1461100,"uid":156327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"法例上張銀紙無爛 銀行就要收"},{"pid":"fd6a935cfc883a6193cf3c0ea348835e2a35c02e","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31025f0ba90573f4e6c213536ed5edbc46523094","tid":1461100,"uid":27436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"睇到好躁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:26:06.000Z","msg":"請大家體諒下 為各巴絲打解釋係需要時間同文字<br />\n<br />\n請大家比機會我為各巴絲服務"},{"pid":"93491356aee25c91e36b4441971efefdb4720760","tid":1461100,"uid":254361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39c6fe6d928baec01e260d7a250463ce4dc1ec08","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"香港有三間發鈔銀行 <br />\n<br />\n匯豐 渣打 及 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中銀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n中銀分行最方便 <br />\n大家可以檢查中銀既銀紙先！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"人地渣打都有相<br />\n你話你自己昨天有張中銀銀紙上有寫野<br />\n咁唔該最少拿張相出黎呀<br />\n有相唔代表係真，但唔該做多重功夫呀"},{"pid":"9de2c4e8ed142c2f98ef9f41beb5b5ec28ada51f","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"367a1baa022941e680fcd21893614e60d3a5dfce","tid":1461100,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />白色恐怖<br />\n佢想凍結你個戶口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:27:30.000Z","msg":"凍結？ 咁又唔會 所有野都唔經你戶口做嫁bo<br />\n<br />\n你只係拎住發鈔銀行既鈔票去更換<br />\n<br />\n遊客見到 佢地都擔心張鈔票用唔用得嫁<br />\n<br />\n難道佢地又有戶口咩？"},{"pid":"ba325f51a25fa2b0aeb5e9c88176f96a7031f1d2","tid":1461100,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:28:24.000Z","msg":"我係中伏撚<br />\n好彩你地夠小心<br />\n唔好入八達通<br />\n唔好入落戶口 找卡數都唔好"},{"pid":"4d0c31ae474159cdeb574dbe2ec79f420e57eb06","tid":1461100,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0712a30aa6a25b125cbe872066c12b4358fd61e2","tid":1461100,"uid":156327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"法例上張銀紙無爛 銀行就要收"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"係呀 為左避免流通紙幣